<subSubSection pageId="103" pageNumber="161" type="activity">
<paragraph blockId="103.[1386,2597,714,1576]" pageId="103" pageNumber="161">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[1386,1623,1188,1221]" pageId="103" pageNumber="161">Activity patterns.</emphasis>
The Kai Flying Fox is nocturnal. It roosts in forested areas with low levels of disturbance.
</paragraph>
